'''Gauntlet Squadron''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] starfighter squadron used in conjunction with [[Corsair Squadron]] during the [[Bacta War]]. It consisted of [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]] and [[A/SF-01 B-wing starfighter/Legends|B-wings]].

When [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] resigned its commission to fight in the Bacta War, Gauntlet Squadron was relied upon heavily by the New Republic to carry out the elite squadron's duties. Gauntlet's [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]] were later assigned to the [[Allegiance (Imperial I-class)|''Allegiance'']] during the hunt for Warlord [[Zsinj]].

During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], Gauntlet Squadron was one of the starfighter squads assigned to the ''[[Soothfast]]'' in the [[Meridian sector/Legends|Meridian sector]]. The squadron took heavy losses at the [[Battle near Exodo II]] but was able to stop the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] from recovering the Priestess [[Elan]].

